 to refreeze the ice blocks after dipping in chocolate, remove them from the freezer 10-20 minutes beforehand to soften to your preferred consistency before serving. Only thaw as many ice blocks as you intend to eat, as refreezing leftovers after they have softened can be a safety hazard."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","7h 15m","6 portions"]}